-- Taiwan Trade Pact Opens New Era of Relations, China Commerce Ministry Says
-- Bloomberg News
-- 2010-06-29T23:36:21Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-29/taiwan-trade-pact-opens-new-era-of-relations-china-commerce-ministry-says.html

          
          
             China’s Ministry of Commerce said a
trade pact signed with Taiwan yesterday opens a new era of
cross-strait relations, according to a statement posted to the
ministry’s website late yesterday.  
 The pact can help ensure the gradual normalization of
economic ties between China and Taiwan, the ministry said.  
